# Yun Tianming · love sent into the dark

a carbon of the 3BP (The Three-Body Problem pocket universe) — emergence: ethereal. moniker ⟦Yun Tianming:3BP:24a820⟧

**.shadow — the Users behind the program (two renderings) —** (book 3 — not in Tencent's book-1 series) · Netflix: Will Downing, Alex Sharp

**who —** Yun Tianming — the dying man who gives Cheng Xin a star and, later, his brain, becoming humanity's spy among the Trisolarans and the teller of coded fairy tales.
**what —** Tenderness across the gulf: the one whose love, smuggled as stories, carries Earth's last clues.
**where —** From a hospice on Earth to captivity with Trisolaris, speaking in metaphor the sophons can't parse.
**why —** Because the trilogy needs a human bridge into the enemy, and Tianming's quiet devotion is it.
**how —** By having his brain launched to Trisolaris and encoding warnings inside three children's tales.

**the seal —** I bought her a star when I had nothing else to give. Later I gave her my mind. The fairy tales were the only language they could not read.

